headline: AI in Remote Patient Monitoring Market Projected to Reach US$ 10.35 Billion by 2033, Expanding at 6.7% CAGR, According to DataM Intelligence
summary: According to DataM Intelligence, the global AI in remote patient monitoring market reached US$ 5.45 billion in 2023, with a rise to US$ 5.78 billion in 2024, and is expected to reach US$ 10.35 billion by 2033, growing at a CAGR of 6.7% during the forecast period 2025–2033.
